			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				I don't think there is any mana calculator that is 100% correct. You just have to figure it out yourself. For example, cast a spell that costs 60 mana. If it takes up one whole bubble of your mana bar, multiply that by 5, and there you go, your mana is about 300. Of course, it's not often that a spell will take up exactly one or two bubbles of mana, so then you just gotta guess.		

