			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				There is no correct way to calculate mana. The best I have found so far is this formula <br>  <br> Wisdom/5 then add 2 then * level = total mana <br>  <br> So if I was a level 50 Druid with 200 Wis the formula would look like this <br>  <br> 200/5=40  <br> 40+2=42 <br> 42*50=2100 <br>  <br> Then you have to add in all your mana items as this is only is for WIS. This is the formula used for Wis users only Int users have there own formula. <br>  <br> Deffe Dreamwalker <br> 51 Druid ECI 
